#: ../../03-workflows.md:1 d7212830a8914ad29148debe11885dd9
msgid "Lazy Todo App — Workflows"
msgstr "Lazy Todo App — 工作流"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:5 2edf7d32875c4af7b4c4437d3b6135ba
msgid "Workflow 1: Todo Lifecycle"
msgstr "工作流 1：Todo 生命周期"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:20 efedc9b413ac481db9bc1bd9c5fc86ec
msgid "Code Path"
msgstr "代码路径"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:22 5ef2842562814e1c8971afd25a4ae030
msgid "`AddTodo.tsx` submits to `useTodos.addTodo()`."
msgstr "`AddTodo.tsx` 提交到 `useTodos.addTodo()`。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:23 719d55bc10b1417593d6f7706bf61d65
#, python-brace-format
msgid "`useTodos` calls `invoke(\"add_todo\", { input })`."
msgstr "`useTodos` 调用 `invoke(\"add_todo\", { input })`。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:24 78f9537d0b644dbe86ed6c7b8640d0d0
msgid "`commands/todo.rs` validates and forwards to `db.rs`."
msgstr "`commands/todo.rs` 完成校验后转发到 `db.rs`。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:25 706d83a12732407f8728fb66f4040422
msgid ""
"`TodoList.tsx` renders active tasks in list or grid mode based on "
"`settings.todo_display`."
msgstr "`TodoList.tsx` 根据 `settings.todo_display` 以列表或网格方式渲染活动任务。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:26 460716599a284a3d887cf6b2725f6bac
msgid ""
"`TodoItem.tsx` uses `useCountdown.ts` to show deadline status in real "
"time."
msgstr "`TodoItem.tsx` 使用 `useCountdown.ts` 实时展示截止时间状态。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:28 16872bf5eb1b4f87a3c72ba67b9bc448
msgid "Workflow 2: Sticky Note Creation and Pop-Out"
msgstr "工作流 2：即时贴创建与弹出窗口"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:41 a223137c7aac49ff8b52ce4555bf3228
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:43 8c41633221c24eeeb703b454623876ec
msgid "`NoteCard.tsx` can still edit inline in the main window."
msgstr "`NoteCard.tsx` 仍然可以在主窗口中进行内联编辑。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:44 a26d0e7c65504ea1886ea2b2ff975d7c
msgid ""
"`NoteWindow.tsx` loads the note by ID using `list_notes` and persists "
"edits through `update_note`."
msgstr "`NoteWindow.tsx` 通过 `list_notes` 按 ID 加载便签，并通过 `update_note` 持久化编辑。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:45 e2662144c38148c5bb7701183b8c4e64
msgid "Markdown is rendered by `MarkdownPreview.tsx`."
msgstr "Markdown 内容由 `MarkdownPreview.tsx` 渲染。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:46 3a232b8728404ddfaf9bb585db0f0c4e
msgid ""
"External links are intercepted in `src/main.tsx` and opened through "
"`@tauri-apps/plugin-shell`."
msgstr "外部链接会在 `src/main.tsx` 中被拦截，并通过 `@tauri-apps/plugin-shell` 打开。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:48 7f5bfde727924507b96df3bba8e34acb
msgid "Workflow 3: Pomodoro Session and Milestones"
msgstr "工作流 3：番茄钟会话与里程碑"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:65 008eed9b3b9048eaa9b4aae534f92b89
msgid "Phase Handling"
msgstr "阶段处理"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:67 e1e69f0259664f63ae5230c79dc5416c
msgid ""
"`usePomodoro.ts` keeps the timer alive even when the Pomodoro tab is "
"hidden."
msgstr "`usePomodoro.ts` 即使在番茄钟标签页被隐藏时也会保持计时器继续运行。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:68 7c9f75dd86d94702b6e6f57d63e0a6be
msgid "Finishing a work phase records a session via `record_pomodoro_session`."
msgstr "完成一个工作阶段后，会通过 `record_pomodoro_session` 记录一次会话。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:69 dd60e4451fa749068a92ac8060267df7
msgid ""
"`PomodoroMilestones.tsx` surfaces up to three active milestones and lets "
"the user mark them as `completed`, `cancelled`, or restored to `active`."
msgstr ""
"`PomodoroMilestones.tsx` 最多展示三个活动里程碑，并允许用户将它们标记为 "
"`completed`、`cancelled`，或恢复为 `active`。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:70 82ec7311ea524ed894667b38f97e5d50
msgid ""
"The backend stores milestone state inside "
"`pomodoro_settings.milestones_json`."
msgstr "后端将里程碑状态存储在 `pomodoro_settings.milestones_json` 中。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:71 e74ed33950bc45479a1df7f6c6aaf0fd
msgid ""
"`update_tray_tooltip` keeps the tray hover text synchronized with the "
"timer."
msgstr "`update_tray_tooltip` 使托盘悬停提示文字与计时器状态保持同步。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:73 64f81d7d591d44c498431dc29e995571
msgid "Workflow 4: Settings Persistence"
msgstr "工作流 4：设置持久化"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:93 cb9355aac683427faf5d60ae2d4b30f9
msgid "Stored Preferences"
msgstr "已存储的偏好项"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:95 9cbb36261d29423a8ab91a4a08490aff
msgid "`page_size`"
msgstr "`page_size`"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:96 03f0e69894b54c3d87d61737a076e333
msgid "`todo_display`"
msgstr "`todo_display`"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:97 223f461291c547bf88f8f783e3ef60e4
msgid "`note_display`"
msgstr "`note_display`"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:98 6b6ac8fef100414a9a1250b42132e4e0
msgid "`note_template`"
msgstr "`note_template`"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:99 c7ba06f695084e2cb0056ee5d202ce3f
msgid "`note_folder`"
msgstr "`note_folder`"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:101 826dd5f5ccbd4bcd82fc57d25f64cb01
msgid "These settings are loaded on app startup via `get_app_settings`."
msgstr "这些设置会在应用启动时通过 `get_app_settings` 加载。"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:103 a9155f0b7a3d4f268f033fe1e0f0dad4
msgid "Workflow 5: System Tray and Window Lifecycle"
msgstr "工作流 5：系统托盘与窗口生命周期"

#: ../../03-workflows.md:117 6e89c957133143b1a8ae1432bd721d2b
msgid "Workflow 6: App Startup"
msgstr "工作流 6：应用启动"

